'''Executioner's Row''' was one of the slums in the city of [[Death (town)|Dying Slowly]] on [[Jubilar/Legends|Jubilar]]. On the edge of the city, it was the home of [[Hallolar Voors]]'s [[Spice/Legends|spice]] warehouse in [[12 BBY/Legends|12 BBY]]. By [[19 ABY/Legends|19 ABY]], the name had apparently fallen into disuse.

